{"ja402:0.1":"Jataka ","ja402:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","ja402:0.3":"Kukkuvagga ","ja402:0.4":"7. Sattubhastajataka ","ja402:1.1":"“Vibbhantacitto kupitindriyosi, ","ja402:1.2":"Nettehi te varigana savanti; ","ja402:1.3":"Kim te nattham kim pana patthayano, ","ja402:1.4":"Idhagama brahme tadingha bruhi”. ","ja402:2.1":"“Miyyetha bhariya vajato mamajja, ","ja402:2.2":"Agacchato maranamaha yakkho; ","ja402:2.3":"Etena dukkhena pavedhitosmi, ","ja402:2.4":"Akkhahi me senaka etamattham”. ","ja402:3.1":"“Bahuni thanani vicintayitva, ","ja402:3.2":"Yamettha vakkhami tadeva saccam; ","ja402:3.3":"Mannami te brahmana sattubhastam, ","ja402:3.4":"Ajanato kanhasappo pavittho. ","ja402:4.1":"Adaya dandam parisumbha bhastam, ","ja402:4.2":"Passelamugam uragam dujivham; ","ja402:4.3":"Chindajja kankham vicikicchitani, ","ja402:4.4":"Bhujangamam passa pamunca bhastam”. ","ja402:5.1":"Samviggarupo parisaya majjhe, ","ja402:5.2":"So brahmano sattubhastam pamunci; ","ja402:5.3":"Atha nikkhami urago uggatejo, ","ja402:5.4":"Asiviso sappo phanam karitva. ","ja402:6.1":"“Suladdhalabha janakassa ranno, ","ja402:6.2":"Yo passati senakam sadhupannam; ","ja402:6.3":"Vivattachaddo nusi sabbadassi, ","ja402:6.4":"Nanam nu te brahmana bhimsarupam”. ","ja402:7.1":"“Imani me sattasatani atthi, ","ja402:7.2":"Ganhahi sabbani dadami tuyham; ","ja402:7.3":"Taya hi me jivitamajja laddham, ","ja402:7.4":"Athopi bhariyaya makasi sotthim”. ","ja402:8.1":"“Na pandita vetanamadiyanti, ","ja402:8.2":"Citrahi gathahi subhasitahi; ","ja402:8.3":"Itopi te brahme dadantu vittam, ","ja402:8.4":"Adaya tvam gaccha sakam niketan”ti. ","ja402:9.1":"Sattubhastajatakam sattamam. "}